{"tid":604957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★跪低！Apple 有意下調今年新 iPhone 發售價！","createTime":"2018-03-25T08:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T04:16:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"849bfd516bf49c2cc21d7a7929bd154a1683de87","tid":604957,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T08:20:01.000Z","msg":"據報道，Digitimes 引用供應鏈的消息指出，其中 5.8 吋的 iPhone Xs 的製造成本顯著降低，預計下降幅度達到 10%。這意味著，在獲利相同的情況下 Apple 可以下調起步價了。而此前有分析機構給出 iPhone X 的成本價估計是 400 美元，所以新品有機會降低到 360 美元。所以這樣一來，5.8 吋新 iPhone 將有可能成為三款中最便宜的一款產品。<br />\n<br />\n總之，在市場上無論售賣任何產品，價格都是顧客購買產品中最直觀一個重要因素，而在影響 iPhone X 熱賣的因素中，價格便是一個主要原因。隨著更多屏幕廠商的加入供應，以及 Face ID 的良率和生產成本的降低，相信 Apple 很可能會動用下調發售價這一個最有效的市場策略來討好消費者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E9%A1%AF%E8%91%97%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E-apple-%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0-iphone-%E7%99%BC%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B9-034036872.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkstylemen.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E8%2591%2597%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BD%258E-apple-%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0-iphone-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%2583%25B9-034036872.html&d=oaWwkkh%2B5ILexk9J9XZkA4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=4456616d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E9%A1%AF%E8%91%97%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E-apple-%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0-iphone-%E7%99%BC%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B9-034036872.html</a>"},{"pid":"ef3c251a9461653ed4cca8fad016ad60d7ddf496","tid":604957,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" c